# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-105">Предотвращение потери данных (DLP) в Центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, что политика DLP ищет при обнаружении каждого типа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-106">This article lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-108">Подтверждающее свидетельство, например ключевые слова и контрольные списки, можно использовать для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-108">Corroborative evidence, like keywords and checksums, can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из этих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-113">Типы конфиденциальной информации используются в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-113">Sensitive information types are used in:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-114">Политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-114">Data loss prevention policies</span></span>](data-loss-prevention-policies.md) 
- [<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-115">Метки конфиденциальности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-115">Sensitivity labels</span></span>](sensitivity-labels.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-116">Метки хранения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-116">Retention labels</span></span>](retention.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-117">Соответствие требованиям к обмену данными</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-117">Communication compliance</span></span>](communication-compliance.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-118">Политики автоматической маркировки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-118">Auto-labelling policies</span></span>](apply-sensitivity-label-automatically.md#how-to-configure-auto-labeling-for-office-apps)

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-119">Номер маршрутки ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-119">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-120">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-120">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-121">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-121">nine digits that may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-122">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-122">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-123">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-123">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-124">четыре цифры, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-124">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-125">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-125">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-126">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-126">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-127">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-127">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-128">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-128">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-129">Неформатированные: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-129">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-130">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-131">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-131">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-132">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-133">Политика имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-133">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-134">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-134">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-135">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-135">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-136">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-136">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-137">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-137">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-143">abarouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-143">abarouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-144">abaroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-144">abaroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-145">americanbankassociationrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-145">americanbankassociationrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-146">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-146">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-147">bankrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-147">bankrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-148">bankroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-148">bankroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-149">routing #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-149">routing #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-152">routing transit number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-152">routing transit number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-153">routing #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-153">routing#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-154">RTN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-154">RTN</span></span>


## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-155">Номер удостоверения личности для Аргентины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-155">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-156">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-157">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-157">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-158">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-159">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-159">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-160">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-160">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-161">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-161">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-162">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-162">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-163">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-163">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-164">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-164">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-165">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-165">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-166">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-166">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-167">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-167">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-168">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-168">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-169">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-169">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-170">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-170">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-176">dni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-176">dni</span></span>

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-182">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-182">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-184">от шести до десяти цифр с номером филиала банковского состояния или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-184">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-186">Номер учетной записи — от 6 до 10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-186">Account number is 6 to 10 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-187">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-187">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-188">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-188">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-189">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-189">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-190">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-190">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-191">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-191">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-192">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-192">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-193">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-193">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-194">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-194">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-195">Регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-195">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-196">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-196">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-197">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-197">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-198">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-198">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-199">Регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-199">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-200">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-200">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-216">Номер компании для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-216">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-217">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-217">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-218">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-218">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-219">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-219">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-220">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-220">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-221">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-221">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-222">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-222">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-223">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-223">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-224">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-224">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-225">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-225">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-226">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-226">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-227">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-227">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-228">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-228">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-229">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-229">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-230">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-230">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-231">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-231">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-232">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-232">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-233">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-233">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-234">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-235">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-235">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-236">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-237">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-238">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-238">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-239">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-239">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-240">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-240">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-241">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-241">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-252">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-252">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-253">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-253">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-254">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-254">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-255">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-255">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-256">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-256">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-257">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-257">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-258">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-258">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-259">девять цифр с делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-259">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-260">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-260">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-261">девять цифр с делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-261">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-262">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-262">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-263">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-263">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-264">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-264">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-265">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-265">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-266">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-266">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-267">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-267">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-268">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-268">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-269">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-269">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-270">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-270">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-271">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-271">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-272">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-272">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-273">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-273">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-274">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-274">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-276">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-276">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-284">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-284">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-285">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-286">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-286">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-287">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-288">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-288">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-289">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-289">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-290">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-290">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-291">пять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-291">five digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-292">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-292">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-293">от одной до двух необязательных букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-293">one to two optional letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-294">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-294">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-295">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-295">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-296">девять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-296">nine digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-297">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-298">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-298">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-299">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-300">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-300">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-301">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-301">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-302">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-302">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-303">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-303">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-403">Номер медицинской учетной записи для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-403">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-404">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-405">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-405">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-406">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-407">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-407">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-408">1-ая цифра находится в диапазоне от 2 до 6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-408">1st digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-409">9-ая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-409">9th digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-410">10-я цифра — это цифра проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-410">10th digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-411">11-я цифра (необязательно) — это индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-411">11th digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-412">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-412">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-413">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-413">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-414">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-414">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-415">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-415">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-416">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-416">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-417">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-417">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-418">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-418">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-419">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-419">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-420">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-420">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-421">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-421">bank account details</span></span>

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-430">Номер паспорта гражданина Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-430">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-431">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-431">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-432">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-432">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-433">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-433">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-434">Буква (без чувствительность к букве), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-434">A letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-435">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-435">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-436">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-436">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-437">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-437">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-438">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-438">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-439">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-439">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-440">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-440">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-474">Номер налогового файла для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-474">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-475">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-476">от восьми до девяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-476">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-477">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-477">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-478">От восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представлены пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-478">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-479">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-479">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-480">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-480">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-481">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-481">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-482">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-482">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-483">две-три цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-483">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-484">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-484">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-485">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-485">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-486">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-486">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-487">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-487">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-488">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-488">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-489">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-489">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-490">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-490">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-502">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-502">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-503">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-503">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-504">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-504">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-505">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-505">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-506">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-506">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-507">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-507">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-508">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-508">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-509">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-509">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-510">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-510">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-511">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-511">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-512">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-512">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-639">Удостоверение личности для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-639">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-640">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-640">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-641">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-641">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-642">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-642">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-643">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-643">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-644">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-644">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-645">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-645">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-646">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-646">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-647">24-значное сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-647">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-648">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-648">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-649">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-649">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-650">22 буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты или знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-650">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-651">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты, знаки плюс или знаки равного знака</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-651">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-653">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-653">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-655">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-655">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-656">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-656">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-657">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-657">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-662">personalausweis repubich österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-662">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-663">Номер паспорта гражданина Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-663">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-664">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-664">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-665">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательное пространство и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-665">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-666">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-666">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-667">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-667">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-668">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-668">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-669">одно пространство (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-669">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-670">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-670">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-671">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-672">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-672">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-673">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-674">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-674">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-675">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-675">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-676">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-676">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-677">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-677">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-678">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-678">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-679">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-679">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-680">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-680">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-681">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-681">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-682">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-682">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-683">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-683">passport#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-690">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-690">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-691">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-691">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-692">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-692">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-693">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-693">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-694">reisepassnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-694">reisepassnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-695">reisepasse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-695">reisepasse</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-696">No-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-696">No-Reisepass</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-697">Nr-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-697">Nr-Reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-698">Reisepass-Nr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-698">Reisepass-Nr</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-701">Номер социального обеспечения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-701">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-702">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-702">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-703">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-703">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-704">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-704">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-705">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-705">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-706">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-706">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-707">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-707">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-708">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-708">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-709">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-709">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-710">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-710">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-711">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-711">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-712">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-712">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-713">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-713">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-714">находится ключевое слово  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` из.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-714">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-715">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-715">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-716">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-716">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-728">socialsecurityno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-728">socialsecurityno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-730">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-730">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-731">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-731">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-732">social security code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-732">social security code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-733">sozialversicherungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-733">sozialversicherungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-734">sozialversicherungsnummer #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-734">sozialversicherungsnummer#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-735">soziale sicherheit kein</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-735">soziale sicherheit kein</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-736">sozialesicherheitkein #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-736">sozialesicherheitkein#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-738">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-738">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-739">versicherungscode</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-739">versicherungscode</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-742">Идентификационный номер налога для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-742">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-743">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-743">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-744">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-744">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-745">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-745">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-746">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-746">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-747">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-747">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-748">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-748">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-749">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-749">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-750">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-750">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-751">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-751">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-752">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-752">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-753">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-753">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-754">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-754">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-755">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-755">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-756">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-756">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-757">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-757">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-758">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-758">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-759">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-759">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-782">Налог на добавленную стоимость для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-782">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-783">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-783">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-784">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-784">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-785">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-785">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-786">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-786">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-787">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-787">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-788">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-788">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-789">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-789">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-790">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-790">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-791">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-791">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-792">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-792">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-793">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-793">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-794">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-794">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-795">Дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-795">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-796">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-796">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-797">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-797">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-798">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-798">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-799">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-799">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-800">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-800">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-801">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-801">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-802">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-802">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-803">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-803">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-804">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-804">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-805">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-805">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-806">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-806">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-807">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-807">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-808">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-808">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-809">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-809">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-810">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-810">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-815">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-815">austrian vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-816">vat no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-816">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-817">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-817">vatno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-819">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-819">austrian vat</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-825">идентификационный номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-825">vat identification number</span></span>
