## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-828">Ключ проверки auth Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-828">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-829">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-829">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-830">Строка DocumentDb, за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-830">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-831">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-831">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-832">Строка DocumentDb</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-832">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-833">Любое сочетание от 3 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-833">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-834">Больше символа (>), знака равного (=), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-834">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-835">Любое сочетание 86 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-835">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-836">Два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-836">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-837">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-837">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-838">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-838">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-839">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-839">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-840">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-840">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-841">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-841">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-842">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-842">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-843">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-843">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-844">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-844">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-845">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-845">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-846">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-846">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-847">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-847">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-848">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-848">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-849">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-849">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-850">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-850">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-851">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-851">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-852">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-852">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-853">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-853">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-854">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-854">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-855">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-855">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-856">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-856">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-857">Строка подключения к базе данных Azure IAAS и строка подключения Azure SQL Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-857">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-858">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-858">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-859">Строка "Server", "server" или "data source", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строку "cloudapp.azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-859">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-860">com или cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-860">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-861">net" или "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-861">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-862">net и строку "Password", "password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-862">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-863">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-863">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-864">строка "Сервер", "сервер" или "источник данных"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-864">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-865">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-865">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-866">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-866">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-867">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-867">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-874">строка "Password", "password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-874">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-875">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-875">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-876">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-876">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-877">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-877">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-879">точка с зачетом (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-879">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-880">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-880">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-881">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-881">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-882">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-882">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-883">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-883">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-884">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-884">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-885">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-885">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-900">Строка подключения Azure IoT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-900">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-901">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-901">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-902">Строка HostName, за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строки "azure-devices".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-902">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-903">net" и "SharedAccessKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-903">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-907">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-907">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-908">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-908">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-909">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-909">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-910">строка "azure-devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-910">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-911">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-911">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-912">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-912">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-913">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-913">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-914">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-914">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-915">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-915">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-916">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-916">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-917">любое сочетание 43 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-917">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-918">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-918">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-921">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-921">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-922">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-922">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

```xml
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-966">Строка подключения кэша Azure Redis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-966">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-967">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-967">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-968">Строка redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-968">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-969">net, за которыми следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку "password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-969">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-970">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-970">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-971">строка redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-971">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-972">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-972">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-973">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-973">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-974">строка "password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-974">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-975">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-975">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-976">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-976">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-977">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-977">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-978">любое сочетание 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком "плюс" (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-978">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-979">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-979">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-980">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-981">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-981">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-982">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-983">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-983">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-984">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-984">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-985">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-985">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-986">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-986">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-987">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-987">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-988">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-988">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-989">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-989">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-990">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-990">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-991">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-991">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-992">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-992">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-993">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-993">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-994">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-994">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-995">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-995">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-996">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-996">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-997">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-997">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-998">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-998">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-999">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-999">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1000">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1000">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1001">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1002">Строка "sig", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1002">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1003">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1003">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1004">строка "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1004">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1005">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1005">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1006">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1006">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1007">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1007">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1008">любое сочетание между 43–53 символами, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1008">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1009">строка "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1009">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1010">любой символ, который не является буквой нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрой или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1010">any character that isn't a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1011">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1011">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1012">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1012">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1013">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1013">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1014">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1014">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1015">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureSAS находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1015">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1016">Строка подключения к шине обслуживания Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1016">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1017">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1017">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1018">Строка "EndPoint", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строки "servicebus.windows".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1018">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1019">net" и "SharedAccesKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1019">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1020">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1020">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1021">строка "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1021">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1022">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1022">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1023">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1023">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1024">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1024">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1025">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1025">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1026">строка "servicebus.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1026">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1027">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1027">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1028">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1028">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1029">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1029">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1030">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1030">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1031">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1031">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1032">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1032">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1033">любое сочетание 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком "плюс" (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1033">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1034">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1034">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1035">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1035">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1036">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1036">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1037">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1037">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1038">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1038">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1039">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1039">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1040">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1040">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1043">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1043">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1049">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1049">localhost</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1055">Ключ учетной записи хранения Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1055">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1056">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1056">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1057">Строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку AccountKey.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1057">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1058">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1058">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1059">строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1059">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1060">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1060">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1061">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1061">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1062">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1062">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1063">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1063">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1064">строка AccountKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1064">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1065">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1065">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1066">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1066">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1067">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1067">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1068">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1068">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1069">два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1069">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1070">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1070">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1071">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1071">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1072">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1072">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1073">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1073">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1074">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1074">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1075">Регулярное выражение CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1075">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1076">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1076">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1094">Ключ учетной записи хранилища Azure (универсальный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1094">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1095">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1096">Любое сочетание 86 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+), предшествующего или за которым следуют символы, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1096">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1097">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1097">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1098">от нуля до одного из символов больше чем (>), апострофа ('), знака равного (=), кавычка (") или знака числа (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1098">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1099">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1099">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1100">два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1100">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1101">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1101">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1102">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1102">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1103">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1103">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1104">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1104">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1105">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1105">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1106">Номер водительского удостоверения для Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1106">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1107">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1107">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1108">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1108">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1109">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1109">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1110">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1110">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1111">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1111">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1112">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1112">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1113">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1113">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1114">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1114">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1115">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1115">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1116">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1116">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1249">Национальный номер для Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1249">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1250">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1250">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1251">11 цифр, а также необязательные селитари</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1251">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1252">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1252">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1253">11 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1253">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1254">шесть цифр и два необязательных периода в формате YY. MM.DD для даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1254">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1255">Необязательный выбор точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1255">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1256">три последовательной цифры (нечетные для самцов, даже для самок)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1256">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1257">Необязательный выбор точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1257">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1258">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1258">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1259">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1259">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1260">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1260">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1261">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1261">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1262">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1262">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1263">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1263">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1264">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_belgium_national_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1264">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1265">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1265">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1266">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1266">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1267">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1267">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1268">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1268">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1327">Номер паспорта гражданина Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1327">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1328">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1328">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1329">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1329">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1330">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1330">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1331">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1331">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1332">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1332">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1333">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1333">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1334">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1334">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1335">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1335">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1336">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1336">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1337">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1337">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1338">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YY или ключевое слово из `Keywords_eu_passport_date` или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1338">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1339">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1339">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1340">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1340">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1341">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1341">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1365">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1365">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1366">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1366">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1367">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1367">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1368">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1368">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1369">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1369">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1370">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1370">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1371">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1371">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1372">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1372">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1373">12-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1373">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1374">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1374">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1375">12-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1375">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1376">буква B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1376">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1377">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1377">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1378">цифра 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1378">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1379">цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1379">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1380">необязательная точка, дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1380">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1381">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1381">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1382">необязательная точка, дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1382">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1383">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1383">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1384">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1384">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1385">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1385">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1386">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1386">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1387">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1387">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1388">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1388">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1389">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1389">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1390">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1390">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1391">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1391">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1403">Номер CPF для Бразилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1403">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1404">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1405">11 цифр, которые включают проверочную цифру и могут быть форматированными или неформатированными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1405">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1406">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1407">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1407">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1408">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1408">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1409">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1409">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1410">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1410">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1411">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1411">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1412">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1412">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1413">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1413">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1414">две цифры, которые являются провероными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1414">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1415">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1415">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1416">11 цифр, где две последние цифры — проверочные.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1416">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1417">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1417">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1418">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1418">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1419">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1419">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1420">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1420">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1421">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1421">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1422">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cpf;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1422">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1423">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1423">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1424">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1424">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1425">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1425">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1426">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1426">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1429">CPF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1429">CPF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1434">Imposto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1434">Imposto</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1435">Identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1435">Identificação</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1436">Inscrição</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1436">Inscrição</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1437">Receita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1437">Receita</span></span> 

   
## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1438">Номер юридического лица для Бразилии (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1438">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1439">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1439">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1440">14 цифр, которые включают регистрационный номер, номер филиала и проверочные цифры, а также разделители.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1440">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1441">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1441">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1442">14 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1442">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1443">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1443">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1444">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1444">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1445">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1445">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1446">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1446">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1447">три цифры (эти первые восемь цифр являются регистрационным номером)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1447">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1448">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1448">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1449">четырехзначный номер филиала</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1449">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1450">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1450">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1451">две цифры, которые являются провероными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1451">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1452">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1452">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1453">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1453">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1454">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1454">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1455">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1455">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1456">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1456">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1457">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cnpj;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1457">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1458">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1458">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1459">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1459">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1460">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1460">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1461">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1461">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1483">Национальный идентификационный номер для Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1483">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1484">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1484">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1485">Registro Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1485">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1486">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1486">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1487">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1487">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1488">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1488">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1489">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1489">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1490">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1490">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1491">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1491">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1492">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1492">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1493">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1493">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1494">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1494">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1495">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1495">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1496">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1496">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1497">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1497">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1498">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1498">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1499">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1499">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1500">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1500">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1501">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1501">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1502">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1502">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1503">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1503">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1504">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1504">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1505">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1505">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1506">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1506">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1507">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1507">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1508">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1508">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1509">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1509">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1510">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1510">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1511">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1511">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1512">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1512">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1513">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1513">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1514">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1514">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1515">RG (это ключевое слово с чувствительностью к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1515">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1516">RIC (это ключевое слово с чувствительностью к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1516">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1517">Номер водительского удостоверения для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1517">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1518">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1518">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1519">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1519">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1520">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1520">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1521">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1521">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1522">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1522">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1523">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1523">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1524">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1524">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1525">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1525">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1526">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1526">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1527">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1527">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```
