## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1654">Однородный номер для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1654">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1655">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1655">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1656">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1656">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1657">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1657">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1658">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1658">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1659">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1659">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1660">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1660">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1661">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1661">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1662">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1662">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1663">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1663">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1664">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1664">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1665">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1665">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1666">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1666">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1667">одна цифра, соответствующая полу: четная цифра для самца и нечетная цифра для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1667">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1668">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1668">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1669">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1669">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1670">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1670">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1671">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1671">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1672">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1672">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1673">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1673">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1674">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1674">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1675">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1675">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1676">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1676">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1721">Номер паспорта гражданина Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1721">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1722">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1722">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1723">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1723">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1724">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1724">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1725">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1725">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1726">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1726">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1727">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1727">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1728">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1728">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1729">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1729">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1730">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1730">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1731">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1731">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1732">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1732">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1733">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1733">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1734">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1734">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1735">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1735">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->

          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1755">Номер банковского счета для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1755">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1756">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1757">7 или 12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1757">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1758">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1759">Номер банковского счета для Канады — 7 или 12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1759">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1760">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1760">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1761">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1761">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1762">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1762">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1763">три цифры ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1763">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1764">ноль "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1764">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1765">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1765">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1766">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1766">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1767">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1767">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1768">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1768">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1769">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1769">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1770">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1770">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1771">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1771">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1772">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1772">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1773">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1773">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1774">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1774">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1775">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1775">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1799">Номер водительского удостоверения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1799">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1800">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1800">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1801">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1801">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1802">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1802">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1803">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1803">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1804">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1805">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1805">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1806">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1807">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1808">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1808">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1809">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1809">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1810">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1810">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1811">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1811">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1951">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1951">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1952">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1952">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1953">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1953">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1954">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1954">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1955">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1955">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1956">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1956">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1968">Номер паспорта гражданина Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1968">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1969">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1969">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1970">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1970">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1971">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1971">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1972">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1972">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1973">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1973">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1974">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1974">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1975">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1975">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1976">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1976">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1977">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1977">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-1978">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-1978">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2014">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2014">No</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2018">Найдено по крайней мере два ключевых Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2018">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2051">Номер социального страхования для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2051">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2052">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2052">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2053">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2053">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2054">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2054">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2055">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2055">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2056">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2056">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2057">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2057">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2058">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2058">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2059">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2059">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2060">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2060">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2061">Неформатированные: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2061">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2062">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2062">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2063">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2063">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2064">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2064">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2065">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2065">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2066">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2066">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2067">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2067">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2068">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2068">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2069">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2069">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2070">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2070">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2071">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2071">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2072">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2072">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2073">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2073">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2074">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2074">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2075">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2075">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2100">Номер удостоверения личности для Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2100">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2101">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2101">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2102">от семи до восьми цифр, а также делегировка контрольной цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2102">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2103">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2103">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2104">семь–восемь цифр, а также делегаторы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2104">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2105">одна–две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2105">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2106">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2106">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2107">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2107">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2108">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2108">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2109">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2109">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2110">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2110">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2111">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2111">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2112">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2112">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2113">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2113">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2114">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2114">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2115">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2115">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2116">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2116">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2117">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2117">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2118">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2118">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2119">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2119">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2120">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2120">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2121">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2121">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2158">Номер удостоверения личности резидента Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2158">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2159">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2159">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2160">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2160">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2161">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2161">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2162">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2162">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2163">шесть цифр, которые являются кодом адреса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2163">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2164">восемь цифр в виде YYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2164">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2165">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2165">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2166">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2166">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2167">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2167">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2168">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2168">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2169">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2169">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2170">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2170">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2171">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2171">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2172">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2172">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2173">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2173">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2174">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2174">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2175">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2175">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2176">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2176">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2189">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2189">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2190">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2190">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2191">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (dddddddd), и которые должны пройти проверку Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2191">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2192">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2192">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2193">Сложный и надежный шаблон, который обнаруживает карточки от всех основных торговых марок по всему миру, включая Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, карточки для карточек.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2193">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2194">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2194">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2195">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2195">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2196">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2196">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2197">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2197">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2198">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2198">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2199">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2199">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2200">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2200">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2201">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2201">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2202">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2202">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2203">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2203">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2204">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2204">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2205">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2205">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2206">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2206">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2466">Номер водительского удостоверения для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2466">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2467">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2467">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2468">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2468">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2469">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2469">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2470">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2470">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2471">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2471">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2472">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2472">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2473">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2473">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2474">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2474">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2475">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2475">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2476">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2476">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2600">Номер удостоверения личности для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2600">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2601">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации для национального идентификационных номеров ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2601">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2602">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2602">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2604">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2604">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2606">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2606">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2607">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2608">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2608">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2609">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2610">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2611">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2611">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2612">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2612">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2643">Номер паспорта гражданина Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2643">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2645">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2645">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2647">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2647">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2648">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2648">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2649">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2649">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2650">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2650">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2651">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2651">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2652">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2652">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2653">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2653">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2654">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2654">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2655">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2655">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2656">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2656">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2657">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2657">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2675">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер (OIB) для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2675">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2676">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2676">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2677">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2677">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2678">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2678">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2679">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2679">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2680">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2680">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2681">окончательная цифра — это провероальная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2681">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2682">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2682">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2683">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2683">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2684">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2684">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2685">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2685">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2686">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2686">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2687">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2687">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2688">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2688">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2689">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2689">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2690">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2690">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2691">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2691">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2722">Номер социального обеспечения хорватии или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2722">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2723">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального обеспечения ЕС или типе конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2723">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2724">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2724">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2725">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2725">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2726">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2726">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2727">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2727">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2728">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2728">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2729">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2729">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2730">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2730">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2731">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2731">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2732">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2732">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2733">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2733">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2734">Функция находит  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2734">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2735">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2735">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2736">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2736">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2737">Функция находит  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2737">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2754">Номер водительского удостоверения для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2754">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2755">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2755">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2756">12 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2756">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2757">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2757">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2758">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2758">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2759">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2759">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2760">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2760">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2761">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2761">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2762">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2762">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2763">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2763">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2764">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2764">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2889">Удостоверение личности для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2889">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2890">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2890">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2891">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2891">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2892">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2892">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2893">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2893">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2894">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2894">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2895">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2895">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2896">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2896">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2897">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2897">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2898">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2898">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2899">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2899">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2900">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2900">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2901">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2901">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2902">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2902">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2903">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2903">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2904">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2904">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2905">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2905">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2906">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2906">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2907">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2907">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2908">id card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2908">id card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2909">номер удостоверения личности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2909">identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2910">kim kimti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2910">kimlik karti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2911">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2911">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2912">личный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2912">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2913">ταυτοτητασ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2913">ταυτοτητασ</span></span>


## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2914">Номер паспорта гражданина Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2914">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2915">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2915">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2916">одна буква, за которой следуют 6–8 цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2916">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2917">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2917">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2918">одна буква, за которой следуют от шести до восьми цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2918">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2919">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2919">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2920">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2920">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2921">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2921">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2922">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2922">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2923">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2923">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2924">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2924">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2925">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД/ММ/YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2925">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2926">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2926">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2927">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2927">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2928">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2928">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2929">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2929">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2957">Идентификационный номер налога на Кипре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2957">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2958">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2958">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2959">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2959">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2960">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2960">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2961">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2961">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2962">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2962">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2963">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2963">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2964">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2964">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2965">восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2965">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2966">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2966">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2967">восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2967">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2968">"0" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2968">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2969">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2969">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2970">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2970">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2971">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2971">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2972">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2972">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2973">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2973">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2974">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2974">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2975">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2975">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2976">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2976">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2977">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2977">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-2978">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-2978">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
