## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3006">Номер водительского удостоверения для Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3006">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3007">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3007">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3008">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3008">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3009">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3009">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3010">восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3010">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3011">буква "E" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3011">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3012">буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3012">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3013">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3013">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3014">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3014">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3015">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3015">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3016">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3016">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3017">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3017">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3018">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3018">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3019">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3019">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3020">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3020">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3146">Номер паспорта гражданина Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3146">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3148">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3148">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3150">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3150">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3151">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3151">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3152">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3152">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3153">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3153">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3154">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3154">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3155">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3155">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3156">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3156">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3157">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3157">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3158">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3158">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3159">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3159">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3160">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3160">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3182">Номер личного удостоверения для Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3182">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3184">девять цифр с необязательной косой чертой (старый формат) 10 цифр с необязательной косой чертой (новый формат)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3184">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3186">девять цифр (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3186">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3187">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3187">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3188">необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3188">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3189">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3189">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3190">10 цифр (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3190">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3191">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3191">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3192">необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3192">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3193">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3193">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3194">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3194">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3195">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3195">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3196">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3196">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3197">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3197">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3198">функция Func_czech_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3198">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3199">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_czech_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3199">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3200">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3200">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3201">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3201">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3202">Функция Func_czech_id_card_new_format находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3202">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3203">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3203">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3250">Чешский номер социального обеспечения или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3250">Czech social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3251">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального обеспечения ЕС или типе конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3251">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3252">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3252">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3253">10 цифр и знаки задней знаки в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3253">10 digits and a backslash in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3254">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3254">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3255">10 цифр и ответная знаки:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3255">10 digits and a backslash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3256">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3256">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD):</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3257">замещенная на задний ряд</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3257">a backslash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3258">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, отделяя людей от одной и той же даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3258">three digits that correspond to a serial number that separates persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3259">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3259">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3260">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3260">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3261">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3261">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3262">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3262">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3263">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3263">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3264">Функция находит  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3264">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3265">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3265">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3266">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3266">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3267">Функция находит  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3267">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3283">Номер водительского удостоверения для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3283">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3284">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3284">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3285">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3285">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3286">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3286">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3287">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3287">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3288">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3288">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3289">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3289">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3290">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3290">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3291">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3291">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3292">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3292">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3293">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3293">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3417">Номер паспорта гражданина Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3417">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3418">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3418">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3419">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3419">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3420">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3420">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3421">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3421">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3422">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3422">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3423">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3423">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3424">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3424">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3425">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3425">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3426">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3426">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3427">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3427">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3428">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3428">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3429">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3429">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3430">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3430">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3431">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3431">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3432">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3432">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3451">Персональный идентификационный номер для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3451">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3452">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3452">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3453">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3453">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3454">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3454">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3455">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3455">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3456">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3456">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3457">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3457">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3458">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3458">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3459">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3460">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3460">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3461">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3462">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3462">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3463">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3463">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3464">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_denmark_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3464">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3465">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3465">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3466">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3466">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3467">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3467">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3468">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3468">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3540">Номер социального обеспечения для Дании или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3540">Denmark social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3541">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только для номера социального обеспечения ЕС или типа конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3541">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3542">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3542">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3543">10 цифр и дефис в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3543">10 digits and a hyphen in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3544">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3544">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3545">10 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3545">10 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3546">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3546">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3547">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3547">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3548">четыре цифры, соответствующие последовательному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3548">four digits that correspond to a sequence number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3549">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3549">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3550">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3550">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3551">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3551">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3552">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3552">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3553">Функция находит  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3553">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3554">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3554">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3555">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3555">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3556">Функция находит  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3556">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3558">Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3558">Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3570">Номер агентства по правоохранительным органам (DEA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3570">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3571">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3571">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3572">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3572">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3573">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3573">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3574">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3574">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3575">одна буква (без регистра) из этого набора возможных букв: abcdefghjklmnprstux, который является кодом регистратора</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3575">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3576">одна буква (без регистра), которая является первой буквой фамилии регистратора или цифрой "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3576">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3577">семь цифр, последняя из которых является провероной.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3577">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3578">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3578">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3579">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3579">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3580">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3580">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3581">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3581">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3582">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3582">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3583">Найдено ключевое `Keyword_dea_number` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3583">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3584">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3584">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3585">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3585">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3586">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3586">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3587">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3587">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3588">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3588">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3589">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3589">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3590">dea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3590">dea</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3592">администрирование принудительных органы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3592">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3593">агентство по правоохранительным органам</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3593">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3594">Номер водительского удостоверения для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3594">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3595">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3595">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3596">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3596">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3597">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3597">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3598">две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3598">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3599">буквы "ET" (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3599">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3600">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3600">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3601">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3601">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3602">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3602">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3603">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3603">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3604">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3604">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3605">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3605">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3606">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3606">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3732">Персональный идентификационный код Для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3732">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3733">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3733">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3734">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3734">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3735">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3735">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3736">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3736">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3737">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3737">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3738">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3738">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3739">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3739">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3740">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3740">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3741">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3741">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3742">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3742">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3743">одна цифра, соответствующая полу и минуте рождения (нечетное число самца, четное число женщина; 1-2: 19-е время; 3-4: 20-й год; 5-6: 21-й год)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3743">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3744">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3744">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3745">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, отделяющие пользователей от одной и той же даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3745">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3746">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3746">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3747">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3747">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3748">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3748">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3749">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3749">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3750">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3750">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3751">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3751">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3752">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3752">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3753">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3753">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3754">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3754">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3787">Номер паспорта гражданина Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3787">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3788">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3788">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3789">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3789">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3790">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3790">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3791">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3791">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3792">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3792">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3793">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3793">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3794">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3794">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3795">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3795">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3796">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3796">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3797">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3797">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3798">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3798">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3799">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3799">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3800">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3800">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3801">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3801">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3819">Номер банковской карты для ЕС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3819">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3820">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3820">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3821">16 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3821">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3822">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3822">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3823">Сложный и надежный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3823">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3824">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3824">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3825">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3825">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3826">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3826">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3827">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3827">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3828">Функция Func_eu_debit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3828">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3829">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3829">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3830">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_eu_debit_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3830">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3831">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3831">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3832">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_security_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3832">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3833">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3833">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3834">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3834">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-3835">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-3835">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4282">Номер водительского удостоверения для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4282">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4283">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4283">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4284">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4284">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4285">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4285">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4286">10 цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4286">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4287">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4287">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4288">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4288">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4289">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4289">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4290">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4290">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4291">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4291">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4292">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4292">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4293">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4293">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4294">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4294">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4295">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4295">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4296">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4296">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4427">Номер медицинского страхования для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4427">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4428">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4428">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4429">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4429">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4430">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4430">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4431">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4431">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4432">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4432">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4433">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4433">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4434">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4434">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4435">20-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4435">20-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4436">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4436">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4437">20-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4437">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4438">10 цифр — 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4438">10 digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4439">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4439">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4440">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4440">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4441">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4441">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4442">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4442">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4443">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4443">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4444">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4444">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4445">Regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4445">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4446">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4446">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4464">Национальный ИД Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4464">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4465">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4465">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4466">шесть цифр плюс символ, указывающий на время года, плюс три цифры плюс провероная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4466">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4467">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4467">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4468">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4468">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4469">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4469">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4470">маркер "-", "+" или "a"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4470">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4471">трехзначный персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4471">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4472">цифра или буква (без чувствительность к делу), которая является проверокой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4472">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4473">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4474">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4474">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4475">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4476">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4476">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4477">функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4477">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4478">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_finnish_national_id,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4478">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4479">контрольнаяума передается</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4479">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4480">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4480">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4481">функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4481">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4482">контрольнаяума передается</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4482">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4531">Номер паспорта гражданина Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4531">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4532">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4532">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4533">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4533">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4534">сочетание девяти букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4534">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4535">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4535">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4536">сочетание из девяти букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4536">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4537">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4537">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4538">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4538">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4539">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4539">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4540">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4540">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4541">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4541">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4542">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4542">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4543">регулярное выражение Regex_finland_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4543">The regular expression Regex_finland_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4544">Находится ключевое слово Keywords_eu_passport_number_common или Keyword_finland_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4544">A keyword from Keywords_eu_passport_number_common or Keyword_finland_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4565">Номер водительского удостоверения для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4565">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4566">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4566">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4567">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4567">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4568">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4568">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4569">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4569">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4570">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4570">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4571">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4571">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4572">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4572">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4573">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4573">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4574">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4574">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4575">функция Func_french_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4575">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4576">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_french_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4576">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
