## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4703">Номер медицинского страхования для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4703">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4704">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4704">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4705">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4705">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4706">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4706">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4707">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4707">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4708">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4708">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4709">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4709">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4710">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4710">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4711">21-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4711">21-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4712">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4712">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4713">21-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4713">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4714">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4714">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4715">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4715">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4716">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4716">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4717">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4717">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4718">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4718">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4719">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4719">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4720">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4720">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4721">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4721">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4722">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4722">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4723">Regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4723">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4724">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4724">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4725">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4725">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4726">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4726">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4730">Национальный удостоверение личности для Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4730">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4731">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4731">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4732">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4732">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4733">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4733">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4734">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4734">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4735">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4735">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4736">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4736">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4737">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4737">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4738">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4738">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4739">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4739">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4740">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4740">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4754">Номер паспорта гражданина Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4754">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4755">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4755">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4756">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4756">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4757">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4757">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4758">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4758">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4759">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4759">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4760">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4760">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4761">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4761">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4762">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4762">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4763">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4763">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4764">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4764">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4765">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4765">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4766">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4766">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4767">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4767">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4768">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4768">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4769">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4769">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4790">Номер социального обеспечения для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4790">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4791">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в номер социального обеспечения ЕС и тип конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4791">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4792">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4792">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4793">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4793">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4794">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4794">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4795">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4795">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4796">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4796">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4797">13 цифр, за которыми следуют пробелы, за которыми следуют две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4797">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4798">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4798">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4799">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4799">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4800">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4800">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4801">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4801">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4802">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4802">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4803">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4803">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4804">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4804">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4805">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4805">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4806">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4806">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4807">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4807">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4808">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4808">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4809">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4809">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4810">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4810">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4811">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4811">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_fr_insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4812">Keyword_fr_insee</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4812">Keyword_fr_insee</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4813">insee</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4813">insee</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4815">securite sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4815">securite sociale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4816">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4816">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4817">national identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4817">national identification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4820">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4820">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4821">d'identité</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4821">d'identité</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4822">numero d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4822">numero d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4823">no d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4823">no d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4824">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4824">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4825">d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4825">d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4826">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4826">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4827">social security code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4827">social security code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4828">social insurance number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4828">social insurance number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4829">le numéro d'identification nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4829">le numéro d'identification nationale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4830">d'identité nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4830">d'identité nationale</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4833">numéro d'assurance sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4833">numéro d'assurance sociale</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4836">Идентификационный номер налога для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4836">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4837">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4837">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4838">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4838">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4839">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4839">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4840">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4840">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4841">Одна цифра, которая должна быть 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4841">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4842">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4842">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4843">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4843">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4844">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4844">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4845">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4845">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4846">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4846">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4847">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4847">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4848">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4848">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4849">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4849">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4850">Три контрольных цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4850">Three check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4851">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4851">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4852">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4852">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4853">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4853">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4854">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4854">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4855">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4855">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4856">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4856">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4857">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4857">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4858">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4858">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4863">tax identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4863">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4864">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4864">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4865">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4865">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4866">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4866">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4867">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4867">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4868">налоговый регистрационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4868">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4869">ыd #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4869">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4870">аdno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4870">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4871">ыdnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4871">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4872">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4872">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4873">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4873">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4874">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4874">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4875">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4875">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4876">tin no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4876">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4877">tin #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4877">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4878">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4878">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4879">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4879">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4880">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4880">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4881">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4881">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4882">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4882">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4883">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4883">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4884">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4884">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4885">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4885">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4886">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4886">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4887">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4887">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4888">13 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4888">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4889">две буквы — FR (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4889">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4890">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4890">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4891">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4891">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4892">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4892">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4893">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4893">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4894">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4894">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4895">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4895">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4896">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4896">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4897">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4897">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4898">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4898">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4899">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4899">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4900">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4900">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4901">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4901">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4902">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4902">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4903">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4903">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4904">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4904">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4905">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4905">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4906">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4906">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4907">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4907">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4908">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4908">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4909">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4909">vat no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4911">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4911">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4912">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4912">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4913">taxe valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4913">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4914">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4914">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4915">n° tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4915">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4916">numéro de tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4916">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4917">numéro d'identification siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4917">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4918">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4918">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4919">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ДЛЯ ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4919">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4920">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4920">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4921">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4922">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4922">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4923">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4924">11 цифр и букв (без чувствительность к буквам):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4924">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4925">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4925">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4926">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4926">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4927">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4927">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4928">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4928">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4929">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4929">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4930">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4930">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4931">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4931">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4932">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4932">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4933">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4933">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4934">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4934">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4935">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4935">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-4936">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-4936">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5085">Номер удостоверения личности для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5085">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5086">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5086">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5087">с 1 ноября 2010 г.: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5087">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5088">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.: 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5088">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5089">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5089">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5090">с 1 ноября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5090">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5091">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5091">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5092">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5092">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5093">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5093">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5094">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5094">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5095">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5095">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5096">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5096">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5097">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5097">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5098">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5098">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5099">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5099">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5100">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5100">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5101">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5101">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5102">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5102">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5103">ausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5103">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5104">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5104">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5105">identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5105">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5106">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5106">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5107">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5107">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5108">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5108">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5109">идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5109">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5110">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5110">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5111">личный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5111">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5112">personalausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5112">personalausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5113">persönliche id nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5113">persönliche id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5114">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5114">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5115">persönliche-id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5115">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5116">Номер паспорта гражданина Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5116">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5117">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5117">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5118">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5118">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5119">10 цифр или букв.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5119">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5120">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5120">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5121">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5121">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5122">первый символ — это цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5122">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5123">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5123">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5124">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5124">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5125">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5125">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5126">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5126">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5127">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5127">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5128">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5128">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5129">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5129">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5130">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5130">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5131">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5131">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5132">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5132">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5133">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5133">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5134">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5134">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5135">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5135">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5136">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5136">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5159">Идентификационный номер налога для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5159">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5160">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5160">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5161">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5161">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5162">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5162">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5163">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5163">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5164">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5164">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5165">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5165">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5166">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5166">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5167">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5167">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5168">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5168">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5169">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5169">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5170">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5170">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5171">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5171">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5172">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5173">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5173">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5174">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5175">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5175">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5176">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5176">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5177">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5177">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5178">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5178">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5179">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5179">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5205">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5205">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5206">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5206">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5207">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5207">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5208">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5208">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5209">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5209">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5210">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5210">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5211">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5211">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5212">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5212">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5213">11 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5213">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5214">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5214">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5215">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5215">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5216">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5216">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5217">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5217">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5218">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5218">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5219">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5219">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5220">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5220">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5221">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5221">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5222">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5222">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5223">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5223">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5224">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5224">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5225">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5225">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5226">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5226">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5227">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5227">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5228">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5228">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5229">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5229">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5230">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5230">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5231">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5231">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5232">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5232">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5233">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5233">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5234">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5234">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5235">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5235">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5236">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5236">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5237">vat# mehrwertsteuer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5237">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5238">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5238">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5239">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5239">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5240">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5240">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5241">Номер водительского удостоверения для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5241">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5242">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5242">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5243">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5243">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5244">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5244">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5245">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5245">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5246">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5246">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5247">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5247">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5248">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5248">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5249">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5249">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5250">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5250">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5251">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5251">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5252">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5252">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5253">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5253">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5261">driver lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5261">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5262">driver lics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5262">driver lics</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5264">driver licenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5264">driver licenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5265">driver licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5265">driver licence</span></span>

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5378">Карточка национального удостоверения личности для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5378">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5379">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5379">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5380">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5380">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5381">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5381">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5382">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5382">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5383">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5383">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5384">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5384">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5385">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5385">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5386">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5386">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5387">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5387">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5388">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5388">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5389">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5389">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5390">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5390">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5391">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5391">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5392">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5392">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5393">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5393">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5394">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5394">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5395">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5395">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5396">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5396">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5397">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5397">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5399">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5399">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5400">греческий ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5400">greek id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5402">личная карточка для греческих личных удостоверений</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5402">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5403">греческий ид полиции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5403">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5404">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5404">identity card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5406">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5406">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5407">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5407">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5408">Номер паспорта гражданина Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5408">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5409">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5409">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5410">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5410">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5411">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5411">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5412">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5412">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5413">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5413">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5414">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5414">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5415">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5415">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5416">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5416">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5417">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5417">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5418">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5418">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5419">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM YY (пример — 28 августа 19) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5419">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5420">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5420">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5421">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5421">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5422">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5422">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5423">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5423">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5424">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5424">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5426">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5426">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5427">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5427">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5428">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5428">passports</span></span>
