- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5431">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5431">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5432">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5432">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5433">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5433">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5434">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5434">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5435">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5435">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5436">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5436">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5437">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5437">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5438">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5438">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5439">Номер социального обеспечения для Греция (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5439">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5440">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5440">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5441">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5441">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5442">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5442">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5443">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5443">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5444">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5444">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5445">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5445">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5446">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5446">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5447">Одиннадцати цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5447">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5448">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5448">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5449">6 цифр в качестве даты рождения YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5449">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5450">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5450">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5451">проверяемая цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5451">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5452">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5452">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5453">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5453">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5454">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5454">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5455">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5455">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5456">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5456">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5457">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5457">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5458">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5458">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5459">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5459">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5460">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5460">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5461">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5461">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5462">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5462">ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5464">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5464">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5465">socialsecurityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5465">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5466">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5466">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5467">amka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5467">amka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5468">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5468">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5469">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5469">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5470">Идентификационный номер налога для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5470">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5471">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5471">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5472">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5472">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5473">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5473">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5474">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5474">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5475">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5475">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5476">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5476">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5477">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5477">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5478">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5478">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5479">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5479">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5480">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5480">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5481">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5481">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5482">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5482">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5483">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5483">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5484">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5484">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5485">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5485">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5486">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5486">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5515">Номер удостоверения личности в Гонконге (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5515">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5516">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5516">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5517">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5517">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5518">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5518">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5519">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5519">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5520">1–2 буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5520">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5521">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5521">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5522">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5522">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5523">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5523">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5524">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5524">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5525">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5525">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5526">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5526">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5527">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5527">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5528">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5528">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5529">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5529">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5530">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5530">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5531">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5531">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5532">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5532">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5572">Номер водительского удостоверения для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5572">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5573">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5573">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5574">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5574">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5575">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5575">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5576">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5576">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5577">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5577">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5578">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5578">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5579">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5580">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5580">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5581">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5582">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5582">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5583">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5583">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5584">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5584">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5717">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5717">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5718">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5718">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5719">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5719">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5720">Одна цифра, соответствующая полу (1- и 2-женская, другая цифра также возможна для граждан, которые раньше 1900 г., или граждан с двойным паспортом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5720">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5721">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5721">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5722">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5722">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5723">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5723">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5724">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5724">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5725">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5725">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5726">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5726">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5727">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5727">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5728">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5728">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5729">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5729">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5730">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5730">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5731">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5731">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5732">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5732">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5733">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5733">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5734">id number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5734">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5735">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5735">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5736">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5736">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5737">sz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5737">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5738">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5738">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5739">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5739">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5740">személyazonosító igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5740">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5741">személyi igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5741">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5742">Номер паспорта гражданина Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5742">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5743">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5743">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5744">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5744">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5745">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5745">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5746">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5746">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5747">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5747">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5748">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5748">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5749">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5749">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5750">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5750">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5751">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5751">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5752">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5752">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5753">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YY (пример — 01 MÁR/MAR 12) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5753">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5754">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5754">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5755">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5755">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5756">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5756">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5757">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5757">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5758">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5758">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5759">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5759">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5760">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5760">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5761">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5761">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5762">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5762">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5763">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5763">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5765">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5765">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5766">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5766">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5767">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5767">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5768">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5768">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5769">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5769">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5770">útlevél száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5770">útlevél száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5771">Útlevelek száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5771">Útlevelek száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5772">útlevél szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5772">útlevél szám</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5773">Номер социального обеспечения для Венгрии (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5773">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5774">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5774">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5775">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5775">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5776">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5776">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5777">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5777">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5778">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5778">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5779">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5779">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5780">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5780">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5781">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5781">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5782">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5782">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5783">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5783">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5784">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5784">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5785">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5785">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5802">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5802">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5805">Идентификационный номер налога для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5805">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5806">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5806">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5807">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5807">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5808">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5808">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5809">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5809">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5810">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5810">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5811">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5811">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5812">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5812">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5813">10 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5813">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5814">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5814">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5815">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5815">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5816">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5816">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5817">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5817">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5818">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5818">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5819">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5819">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5820">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5820">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5821">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5821">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5822">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5822">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5823">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5823">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5824">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5824">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5825">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5825">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5826">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5826">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5829">adóazonosító szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5829">adóazonosító szám</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5838">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5838">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5841">налоговый регистрационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5841">tax registration number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5845">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5845">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5846">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5846">taxnumber#</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5852">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5852">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5853">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5853">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5854">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5854">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5855">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5855">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5856">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5856">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5857">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5857">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5858">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5858">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5859">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5860">10 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5860">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5861">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5862">10 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5862">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5863">две буквы — HU или hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5863">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5864">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5864">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5865">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5865">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5866">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5866">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5867">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5867">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5868">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5868">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5869">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5869">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5870">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5870">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5871">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5871">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5872">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5872">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5873">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5873">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5874">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5874">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5875">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5875">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5876">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5876">vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5877">номер налога на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5877">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5878">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5878">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5879">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5879">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5880">hungarianvatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5880">hungarianvatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5881">tax no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5881">tax no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5882">налог на добавленную стоимость ( áfa)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5882">value added tax áfa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5883">közösségi adószám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5883">közösségi adószám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5884">általános forgalmi adó szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5884">általános forgalmi adó szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5885">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5885">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5886">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5886">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5887">Постоянный номер учетной записи Для Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5887">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5888">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5888">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5889">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5889">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5890">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5890">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5891">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5891">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5892">Три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5892">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5893">Буква в C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5893">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5894">Буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5894">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5895">Четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5895">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5896">Буква, которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5896">A letter that is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5897">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5897">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5898">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5898">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5899">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5899">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5900">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5900">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5901">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5901">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5902">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5902">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5903">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5903">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5904">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5904">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5905">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5905">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5906">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5906">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5907">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5907">Permanent Account Number</span></span>

## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5909">Уникальный идентификационный номер (Aadhaar) для Индии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5909">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5910">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5910">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5911">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5911">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5912">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5912">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5913">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5913">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5914">Цифра, которая не является 0 или 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5914">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5915">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5915">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5916">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5916">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5917">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5917">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5918">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5918">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5919">Последняя цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5919">The final digit, which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5920">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5920">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5921">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5921">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5922">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5922">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5923">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5923">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5924">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5924">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5925">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5925">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5926">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5926">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5927">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5927">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5928">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5928">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5929">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5929">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5930">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5930">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5931">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5931">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5932">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5932">aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5933">aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5933">aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5934">aadhar #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5934">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5935">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5935">uid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5936">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5936">आधार</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5937">uidai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5937">uidai</span></span>
   
## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5938">Номер удостоверения личности (KTP) для Индонезии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5938">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5939">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5939">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5940">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5940">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5941">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5941">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5942">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5942">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5943">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5943">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5944">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5944">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5945">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5945">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5946">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5946">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5947">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5947">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5948">Шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5948">Six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5949">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5949">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5950">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5950">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5951">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5951">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5952">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5952">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5953">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5953">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5954">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5954">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5955">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5955">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5956">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5956">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5957">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5957">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5958">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5958">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5959">KTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5959">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5960">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5960">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5961">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5961">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5962">Международный номер банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5962">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5963">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5963">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5964">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5964">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5965">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5965">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5966">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5966">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5967">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5967">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5968">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5968">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5969">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5969">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5970">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5970">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-p138">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-p138">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5973">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5973">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5974">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5974">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5975">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5975">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5976">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5976">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5977">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5977">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5978">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5978">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5979">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5979">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5980">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5980">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5981">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5981">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5982">Международная классификация болезни (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5982">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5983">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5983">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5984">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5984">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5985">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5985">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5986">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5986">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5987">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5987">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5988">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5988">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5989">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5989">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5990">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5990">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5991">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5991">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5992">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5992">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5993">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5993">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5994">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_, обновленное.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5994">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-5995">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-5995">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6000">Международная классификация болезни (ICD-9-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6000">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6001">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6002">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6002">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6003">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6003">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6004">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6004">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6005">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6005">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6006">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6006">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6007">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6007">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6008">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6008">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6009">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6009">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6010">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6010">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6011">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6011">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6012">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6012">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6013">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6013">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6014">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Девятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6014">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6015">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не страховые коды.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6015">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6016">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_codes ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Девятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6016">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6017">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6017">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6018">IP-адрес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6018">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6019">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6019">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6020">IPv4:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6020">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6021">Сложный шаблон, учитывая форматированные (периоды) и неформатированные (без периодов) версии IPv4-адресов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6021">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6022">IPv6:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6022">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6023">Сложный шаблон, который учитывает форматированные номера IPv6 (включая двоеточия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6023">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6024">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6024">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6025">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6026">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6026">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6027">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6028">Для IPv6 политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6028">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6029">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6029">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6030">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6030">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6031">В случае с протоколом IPv4 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6031">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6032">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6032">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6033">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6033">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6034">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6034">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6035">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6035">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6036">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6036">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6037">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6037">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ipaddress"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6038">Keyword_ipaddress</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6038">Keyword_ipaddress</span></span>
