- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6040">ip address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6040">ip address</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6041">ip addresses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6041">ip addresses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6042">internet protocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6042">internet protocol</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6044">Номер водительского удостоверения для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6044">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6045">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6045">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6046">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6046">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6047">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6047">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6048">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6048">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6049">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6049">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6050">Четыре буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6050">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6051">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6051">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6052">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6052">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6053">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6053">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6054">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6055">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6055">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6056">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6056">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6180">Номер паспорта гражданина Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6180">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6181">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6181">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6182">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6182">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6183">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6183">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6184">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6184">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6185">Две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6185">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6186">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6186">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6187">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6187">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6188">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6188">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6189">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6189">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6190">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6190">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6191">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6191">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6192">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6192">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6193">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 BEA/MAY 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6193">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6194">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6194">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6195">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6195">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6196">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6196">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6197">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6197">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6220">Номер личной службы (PPS) для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6220">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6221">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6222">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6222">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6223">семь цифр, за которыми следуют 1–2 буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6223">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6224">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6224">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6225">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6225">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6226">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6226">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6227">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6227">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6228">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6228">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6229">от одной до двух букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6229">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6230">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6230">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6231">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6231">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6232">буква (без регистрации буквы), которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6232">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6233">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A-I или W</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6233">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6234">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6235">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6235">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6236">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6237">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6238">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6238">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6239">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6239">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6240">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6240">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6241">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6241">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6242">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6242">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6243">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6243">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6288">Номер банковского счета для Израиль</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6288">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6289">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6290">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6290">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6291">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6292">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6292">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6293">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6293">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6294">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6294">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6295">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6295">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6296">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6296">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6297">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6297">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6298">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6298">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6299">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6299">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6300">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6300">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6301">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6301">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6302">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6302">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6303">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6303">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6304">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6304">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6305">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6305">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6306">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6306">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6307">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6307">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6308">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6308">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6309">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6309">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6310">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6310">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6311">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6311">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6312">Национальный идентификационный номер для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6312">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6313">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6313">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6314">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6314">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6315">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6315">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6316">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6316">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6317">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6317">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6318">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6318">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6319">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6319">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6320">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6320">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6321">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6321">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6322">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6322">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6323">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6323">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6326">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6326">מספר זהות</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6328">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6328">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span></span>      
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6329">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6329">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6330">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6330">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6331">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6331">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6332">رقم الهوية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6332">رقم الهوية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6333">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6333">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6334">idnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6334">idnumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6335">id number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6335">id number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6336">identity no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6336">identity no</span></span>        
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6337">identitynumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6337">identitynumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6338">идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6338">identity number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6339">многоядерный объект</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6339">israeliidentitynumber</span></span>       
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6340">личный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6340">personal id</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6341">уникальный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6341">unique id</span></span>  

   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6342">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6342">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6343">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6343">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6344">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6344">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6345">сочетание 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6345">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6346">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6346">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6347">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6347">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6348">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6348">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6349">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6349">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6350">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6350">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6351">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6351">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6352">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6352">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6353">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6353">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6354">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6354">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6355">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6355">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6356">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6356">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6357">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6357">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6358">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6358">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6359">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6359">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6360">numero di patente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6360">numero di patente</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6361">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6361">patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6362">patente guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6362">patente guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6363">patenti di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6363">patenti di guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6364">patenti guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6364">patenti guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6365">Финансовый код Для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6365">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6366">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6366">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6367">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6367">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6368">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6368">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6369">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6369">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6370">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6370">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6371">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6371">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6372">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6372">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6373">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6373">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6374">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6374">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6375">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6375">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6376">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6376">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6377">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6377">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6378">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6378">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6379">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, — буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A к E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6379">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6380">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6380">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6381">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, определенному для страны, где был человек ( коды для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6381">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6382">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6382">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6383">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6383">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6384">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6384">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6385">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6385">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6386">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6386">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6387">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6387">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6388">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6388">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6389">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6389">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6390">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6390">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6391">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6391">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6392">Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6392">Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6393">codice fiscal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6393">codice fiscal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6395">codice id personale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6395">codice id personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6396">codice personale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6396">codice personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6397">финансовый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6397">fiscal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6398">numero certificato personale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6398">numero certificato personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6399">numero di identificone fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6399">numero di identificazione fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6400">numero id personale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6400">numero id personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6401">numero personale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6401">numero personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6402">личный номер сертификата</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6402">personal certificate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6403">личный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6403">personal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6404">код личного кода</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6404">personal id code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6405">личный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6405">personal id number</span></span>

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6425">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6425">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6426">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6426">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6427">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6427">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6428">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6428">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6429">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6429">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6430">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6430">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6431">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6431">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6432">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6432">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6433">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6433">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6434">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6434">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6435">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6435">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6436">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6436">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6437">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6438">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6438">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6439">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6439">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6440">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6440">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6441">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6441">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6447">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6447">passports</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6454">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6454">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6465">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6465">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6466">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6466">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6467">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6467">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6468">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6468">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6469">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6469">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6470">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6470">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6471">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6471">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6472">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6472">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6473">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6473">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6474">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6474">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6475">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными разнородных символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6475">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6476">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6476">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6477">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6477">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6478">необязательное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6478">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6479">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6479">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6480">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6480">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6481">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6481">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6482">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6482">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6483">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6483">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6484">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6484">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6485">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6485">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6486">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6486">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6487">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6487">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6489">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6489">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6495">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6495">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6496">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6496">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6497">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6497">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6498">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6498">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6499">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6499">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6500">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6500">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6501">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6501">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6502">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6502">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6503">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6503">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6504">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6504">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6505">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6505">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6506">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6506">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6507">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6507">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6508">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6508">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6509">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6509">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6510">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6510">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6511">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6511">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6512">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6512">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6513">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6513">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6514">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6514">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6515">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6515">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6516">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6516">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6563">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6563">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6564">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6564">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6565">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6565">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6566">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6566">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6567">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6567">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6568">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6568">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6569">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6569">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6570">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6570">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6571">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6571">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6572">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6572">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6573">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6573">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6615">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6615">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6616">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6616">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6617">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6617">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6618">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6619">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6619">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6620">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6621">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6621">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6622">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6622">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6623">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6623">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6624">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6624">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6625">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6625">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6626">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6626">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6627">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6627">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6628">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6628">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6629">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6629">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6630">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6630">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6631">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6631">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6632">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6632">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6633">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6633">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6634">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6634">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6635">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6635">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6636">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6636">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6637">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6637">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6638">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6638">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6639">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6639">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6640">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6640">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6641">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6641">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6642">法人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6642">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6643">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6643">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6644">Мой номер для Японии — личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6644">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6645">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6645">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6646">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6646">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6647">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6647">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6648">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6648">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6649">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6649">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6650">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6650">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6651">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6651">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6652">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6652">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6653">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6653">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6654">12-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6654">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6655">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6655">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6656">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6656">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6657">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6657">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6658">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6658">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6659">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6659">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6660">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6660">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6661">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6661">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6662">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6662">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6663">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6663">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6664">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6664">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6665">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6665">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6666">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6666">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6667">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6667">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6668">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6668">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6673">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6673">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6674">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6674">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6675">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6675">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6676">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6676">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6677">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6677">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6678">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6678">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6679">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6679">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6680">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6680">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6681">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6681">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6682">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6682">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6683">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6683">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6684">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6684">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6685">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6685">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6686">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6686">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6687">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6687">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6688">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6688">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6689">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6689">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6690">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6690">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6692">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6692">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6697">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6697">パスポート</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6699">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6699">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6700">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6700">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6701">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6701">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6702">パポ>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6702">パスポートNo.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6704">旅券番号＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6704">旅券番号＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6705">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6705">旅券番号♯</span></span>
