## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6707">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6707">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6708">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6709">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6709">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6710">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6710">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6711">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6711">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6712">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6712">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6713">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6713">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6714">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6714">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6715">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6716">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6716">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6717">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6718">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6718">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6719">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6719">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6720">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6720">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6721">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6721">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6722">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6722">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6723">Номер карты для проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6723">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6724">Карты проживания нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6724">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6725">Карточка для проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6725">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6726">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6726">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6727">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6727">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6728">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6728">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6729">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6729">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6730">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6730">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6731">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6731">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6732">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6732">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6733">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6733">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6734">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6734">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6735">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6735">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6736">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6736">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6737">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6737">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6738">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6738">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6739">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6739">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6740">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6740">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6741">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6741">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6742">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6742">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6743">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6743">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6744">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6744">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6745">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6745">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6746">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6746">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6747">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6747">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6748">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6748">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6749">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6749">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6750">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6750">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6751">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6751">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6752">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6752">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6753">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6753">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6754">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6754">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6755">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6755">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6756">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6756">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6757">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6757">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6758">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6758">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6759">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6759">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6760">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6760">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6761">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6762">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6762">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6763">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6764">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6764">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6765">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6765">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6766">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6766">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6767">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6767">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6768">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6768">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6769">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6769">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6782">社会保険No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6782">社会保険No.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6784">介護保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6784">介護保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6785">介護保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6785">介護保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6786">健康保険被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6786">健康保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6787">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6787">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6788">厚生年金</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6788">厚生年金</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6789">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6789">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span></span>


## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6790">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6790">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6791">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6791">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6792">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6792">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6793">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6793">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6794">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6794">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6795">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6795">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6796">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6796">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6797">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6797">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6798">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6798">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6799">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6799">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6800">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6800">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6801">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6801">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6802">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6802">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6803">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6803">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6808">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6808">driverlicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6809">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6809">driverlicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6810">driverlicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6810">driverlicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6811">driver lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6811">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6812">driver lics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6812">driver lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6813">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6813">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6814">driver licenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6814">driver licenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6815">driver licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6815">driver licence</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6927">Персональный код для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6927">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6928">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6928">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6929">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6929">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6930">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6930">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6931">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6931">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6932">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6932">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6933">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6933">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6934">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6934">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6935">одна цифра, соответствующая годовщине рождения ("0" для 19-го, "1" для 20-го и "2" для 21-го)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6935">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6936">четыре цифры, генерируемые случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6936">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6937">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6937">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6938">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6938">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6939">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6939">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6940">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6940">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6941">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6941">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6942">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6942">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6943">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6943">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6944">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6944">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6945">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6945">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6946">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6946">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6947">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6947">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-6948">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-6948">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7011">Номер паспорта гражданина Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7011">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7012">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7012">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7013">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7013">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7014">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7014">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7015">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7015">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7016">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7016">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7017">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7017">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7018">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7018">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7019">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7019">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7020">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7020">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7021">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7021">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7022">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7022">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7023">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7023">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7024">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7024">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7025">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7025">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7026">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7026">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7027">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7027">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7040">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7040">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7041">pase nu nu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7041">pase numurs</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7042">pase nu nu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7042">pase numur</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7043">pases numuri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7043">pases numuri</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7044">pases nr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7044">pases nr</span></span>

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7050">Номер водительского удостоверения для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7050">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7051">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7051">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7052">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7052">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7053">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7053">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7054">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7054">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7055">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7055">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7056">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7056">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7057">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7057">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7058">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7058">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7059">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7059">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7060">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7060">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7185">Персональный код Для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7185">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7186">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7186">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7187">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7187">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7188">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7188">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7189">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7189">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7190">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7190">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7191">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7191">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7192">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7192">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7193">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7193">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7194">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7194">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7195">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7195">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7196">одна цифра (1–6), соответствующая полу и возрасту человека при рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7196">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7197">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7197">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7198">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7198">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7199">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7199">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7200">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7201">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7201">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7202">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7203">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7204">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7204">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7205">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7205">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7206">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7206">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7207">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7207">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7242">Номер паспорта гражданина Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7242">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7243">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7243">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7244">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7244">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7245">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7245">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7246">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7246">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7247">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7247">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7248">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7248">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7249">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7249">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7250">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7250">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7251">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7251">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7252">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7252">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7253">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7253">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7254">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7254">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7255">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7255">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7256">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7256">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7257">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7257">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7258">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7258">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7267">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7267">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7268">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7268">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7269">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7269">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7276">Номер водительского удостоверения Химнюка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7276">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7277">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7277">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7278">шесть цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7278">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7279">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7279">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7280">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7280">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7281">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7281">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7282">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7282">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7283">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7283">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7284">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7284">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7285">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7285">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7286">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7286">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7410">Национальный идентификационный номер (естественные лица) для Нюксемнеса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7410">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7411">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7411">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7412">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7412">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7413">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7413">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7414">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7414">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7415">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7415">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7416">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7416">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7417">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7417">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7418">13 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7418">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7419">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7419">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7420">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7420">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7421">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7421">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7422">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7422">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7423">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7424">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7424">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7425">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7426">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7426">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7427">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7427">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7428">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7428">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7429">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7429">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7430">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7430">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7453">Номер паспорта Химмхета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7453">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7454">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7454">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7455">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7455">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7456">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7456">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7457">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7457">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7458">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7458">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7459">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7459">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7460">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7460">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7461">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7461">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7462">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7462">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7463">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7463">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7464">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7464">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7465">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7465">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7466">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7466">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7467">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7467">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7497">дата проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7497">date of issue</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7499">Идентификационный номер национального идентификации для Нюмнеса (не является естественным лицом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7499">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7500">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7500">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7501">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7501">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7502">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7502">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7503">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7503">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7504">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7504">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7505">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7505">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7506">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7506">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7507">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7507">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7508">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7508">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7509">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7509">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7510">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7510">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7511">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7511">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7512">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7512">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7513">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7513">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7514">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7514">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7515">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7515">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7516">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7516">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7517">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7517">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7518">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7518">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7519">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7519">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7559">Номер идентификационных карт для Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7559">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7560">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7560">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7561">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7561">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7562">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7562">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7563">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7563">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7564">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7564">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7565">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7565">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7566">двух буквный код места рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7566">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7567">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7567">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7568">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7568">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7569">однозначный код пола</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7569">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7570">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7570">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7571">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7571">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7572">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7572">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7573">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7573">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7574">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7574">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7575">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7575">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7601">личная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7601">personal identification card</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7602">Номер водительского удостоверения для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7602">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7604">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7604">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7606">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7606">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7607">два символа (цифры или буквы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7607">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7608">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7608">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7609">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7609">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7610">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7610">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7611">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7611">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7612">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7612">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7613">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7613">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7614">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7614">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7615">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7615">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7616">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7616">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7617">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7617">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7741">Номер удостоверения личности для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7741">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7742">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7742">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7743">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7743">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7744">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7744">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7745">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7745">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7746">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7746">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7747">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7747">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7748">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7748">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7749">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7749">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7750">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7750">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7751">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7751">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7752">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7752">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7753">одна буква в "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без чувствительность к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7753">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7754">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7754">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7755">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7755">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7756">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7756">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7757">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7757">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7758">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7758">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7759">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7759">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7760">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7760">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7761">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7761">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7763">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7763">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7767">kodiċi numerali personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7767">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7769">numru ta 'identifzzjonident-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7769">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7770">numru ta 'identifzzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7770">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7771">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7771">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7772">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7772">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7773">numruru-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7773">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7777">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7777">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>


## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7778">Номер паспорта гражданина Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7778">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7779">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7779">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7780">семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7780">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7781">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7781">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7782">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7782">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7783">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7783">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7784">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7784">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7785">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7785">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7786">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7786">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7787">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7787">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7788">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7788">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7789">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7789">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7790">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7790">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7791">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7791">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7792">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7792">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7802">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7802">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7803">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7803">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7804">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7804">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7805">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7805">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7806">numru tal-passaport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7806">numru tal-passaport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7807">numri tal-passaport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7807">numri tal-passaport</span></span>
