## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7812">Идентификационный номер налога на Мальте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7812">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7813">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7813">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7814">Для граждан Тайваня:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7814">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7815">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7815">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7816">Неконтюзские граждане и подмайства:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7816">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7817">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7817">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7818">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7818">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7819">Граждане Тайваня: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7819">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7820">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7820">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7821">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7821">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7822">Негитюзские граждане и сущностями, не относягими к сущностям: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7822">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7823">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7823">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7824">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7824">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7825">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7825">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7826">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7826">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7827">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7827">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7828">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7828">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7829">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7829">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7830">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7830">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7831">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7831">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7864">Номер службы гражданина Нидерландов (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7864">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7865">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7865">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7866">восемь или девять цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7866">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7867">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7867">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7868">восемь-девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7868">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7869">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7869">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7870">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7870">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7871">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7871">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7872">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7872">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7873">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7873">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7874">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7874">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7875">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7875">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7876">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7876">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7877">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7877">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7878">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7878">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7879">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7879">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7880">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7880">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7900">uniek identiteitsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7900">uniek identiteitsnummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7903">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7903">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7904">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7904">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7905">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7905">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7906">десять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7906">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7907">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7907">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7908">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7908">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7909">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7909">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7910">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7910">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7911">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7911">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7912">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7912">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7913">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7913">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-7914">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-7914">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8042">Номер паспорта гражданина Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8042">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8043">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8043">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8044">девять букв или цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8044">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8045">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8045">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8046">девять букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8046">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8047">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8047">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8048">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8048">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8049">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8049">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8050">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8050">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8051">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8051">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8052">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8052">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8053">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YYYY (пример — 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8053">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8054">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8055">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8055">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8056">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8056">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8074">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8074">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8075">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8075">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8076">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8076">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8077">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8077">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8078">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8078">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8079">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8079">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8080">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8080">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8081">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8081">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8082">девять цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8082">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8083">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8083">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8084">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8084">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8085">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8085">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8086">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8086">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8087">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8087">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8088">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8088">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8089">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8089">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8090">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8090">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8091">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8091">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8092">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8092">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8130">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8130">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8131">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8131">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8132">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8132">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8133">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8133">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8134">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8134">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8135">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8135">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8136">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8136">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8137">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8137">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8138">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8138">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8139">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8139">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8140">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8140">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8141">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8141">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8142">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8142">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8143">необязательное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8143">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8144">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8144">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8145">необязательное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8145">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8146">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8146">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8147">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8147">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8148">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8148">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8149">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8149">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8150">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8150">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8151">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8151">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8152">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8152">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8153">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8153">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8154">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8154">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8155">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8155">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8156">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8156">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8157">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8157">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8158">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8158">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8159">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8159">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8160">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8160">vat#</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8164">Номер банковского счета для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8164">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8165">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8165">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8166">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8166">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8167">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8167">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8168">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8168">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8169">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8169">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8170">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8170">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8171">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8171">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8172">От 14 до 16-значного шаблона с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8172">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8173">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8173">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8174">От 14 до 16-значного шаблона с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8174">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8175">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8175">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8176">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8176">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8177">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8177">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8178">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8178">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8179">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8179">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8180">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8180">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8181">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8181">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8182">дефис или пробел для параметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8182">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8183">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8183">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8184">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8184">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8185">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8185">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8186">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8186">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8187">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8187">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8188">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8188">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8189">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8189">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8190">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8190">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8198">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8198">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8199">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8199">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8200">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8200">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8201">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8201">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8202">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8202">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8203">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8203">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8204">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8204">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8205">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8205">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8206">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8206">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8207">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8207">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8208">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8208">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8209">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8209">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8210">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8210">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8211">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8211">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8212">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8212">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8213">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8213">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8214">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8214">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8215">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8215">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8216">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8216">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8217">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8217">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8218">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8218">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8285">Число внутренних доходов для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8285">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8286">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8286">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8287">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8287">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8288">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8288">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8289">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8289">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8290">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8290">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8291">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8291">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8292">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8292">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8293">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8293">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8294">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8294">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8295">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8295">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8296">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8296">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8297">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8297">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8298">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8298">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8299">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8299">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8300">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8300">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8301">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8301">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8302">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8302">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8303">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8303">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8304">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8304">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8305">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8305">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8306">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8306">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8307">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8307">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8308">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8308">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8309">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8309">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8310">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8310">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8311">ird no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8311">ird no.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8313">nz ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8313">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8314">новая Зеландия ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8314">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8315">ird number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8315">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8316">inland revenue number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8316">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8317">Министерство здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8317">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8318">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8318">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8319">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8319">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8320">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8320">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8321">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8321">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8322">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8322">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8323">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8323">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8324">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8324">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8325">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8325">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8326">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8326">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8327">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8327">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8328">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8328">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8329">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8329">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8330">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8330">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8331">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8331">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8332">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8332">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8333">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8333">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8334">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8334">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8335">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8335">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8336">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8336">NHI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8339">обработка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8339">treatment</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8340">National Health Index Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8340">National Health Index Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8341">nhi number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8341">nhi number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8342">nhi no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8342">nhi no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8343">NHI #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8343">NHI#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8344">National Health Index No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8344">National Health Index No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8345">National Health Index Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8345">National Health Index Id</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8347">Номер социальных сетей Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8347">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8348">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8348">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8349">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8349">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8350">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8350">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8351">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8351">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8352">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8352">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8353">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8353">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8354">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8354">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8355">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8355">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8356">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8356">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8357">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8357">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8358">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8358">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8359">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8359">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8360">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8360">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8361">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8361">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8362">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8362">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8363">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8363">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8364">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8364">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8365">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8365">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8366">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8366">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8367">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8367">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8368">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8368">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8369">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8369">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8370">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8370">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8378">Идентификационный номер для Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8378">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8379">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8379">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8380">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8380">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8381">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8381">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8382">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8382">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8383">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8383">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8384">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8384">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8385">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8385">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8386">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8386">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8387">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8387">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8388">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8388">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8389">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8389">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8390">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8390">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8391">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8391">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8392">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8392">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8393">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8393">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8394">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8394">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8395">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8395">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8400">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8400">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8401">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8401">Identification</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8404">Единый многонамерный идентификационный номер для Филиппин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8404">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8405">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8405">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8406">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8406">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8407">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8407">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8408">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8408">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8409">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8409">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8410">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8410">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8411">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8411">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8412">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8412">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8413">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8413">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8414">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8414">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8415">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8415">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8416">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8416">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8417">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8417">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8418">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8418">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8419">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8419">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8420">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8420">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8421">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8421">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8422">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8422">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8426">Номер водительского удостоверения для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8426">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8427">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8427">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8428">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косые черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8428">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8429">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8429">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8430">14 цифр и 2 косой черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8430">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8431">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8431">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8432">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8432">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8433">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8433">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8434">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8434">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8435">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8435">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8436">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8436">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8437">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8437">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8438">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8438">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8439">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8439">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8440">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8440">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8441">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8441">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8565">Удостоверение личности для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8565">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8566">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8566">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8567">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8567">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8568">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8568">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8569">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8569">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8570">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8570">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8571">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8571">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8572">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8572">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8573">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8573">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8574">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8574">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8575">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8575">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8576">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8576">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8577">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8577">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8578">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8578">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8579">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8579">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8580">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8580">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8581">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8581">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8582">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8582">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8583">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8583">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8584">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8584">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8585">dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8585">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8586">os.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8586">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8587">Национальный ИД для Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8587">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8588">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8588">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8589">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8589">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8590">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8590">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8591">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8591">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8592">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8592">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8593">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8593">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8594">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8594">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8595">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8595">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8596">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8596">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8597">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8597">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8598">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8598">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8599">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8599">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8600">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8600">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8601">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8601">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8602">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8602">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8603">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8603">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8604">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8604">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8613">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8613">pesel</span></span>
