## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8615">Номер паспорта гражданина Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8615">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8616">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8616">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8617">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8617">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8618">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8619">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8619">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8620">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8621">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8621">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8622">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8622">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8623">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8623">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8624">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8624">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8625">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8625">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8626">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8626">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8627">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8627">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8628">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8628">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8629">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8629">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8630">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8630">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8631">Numer paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8631">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8632">Nr.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8632">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8633">Paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8633">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8634">Paszport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8634">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8635">Номер REGON для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8635">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8636">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8636">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8637">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8637">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8638">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8638">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8639">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8639">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8640">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8640">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8641">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8641">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8642">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8642">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8643">9-значный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8643">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8644">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8644">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8645">девятизначное или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8645">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8646">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8646">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8647">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8647">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8648">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8648">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8649">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8649">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8650">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8650">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8651">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8651">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8652">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8652">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8653">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8653">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8654">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8654">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8655">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8655">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8656">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8656">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8657">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8657">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_poland_regon_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8659">Keywords_poland_regon_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8659">Keywords_poland_regon_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8663">статистический нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8663">statistical no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8666">regonno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8666">regonno#</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8674">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8674">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8675">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8675">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8676">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8676">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8677">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8677">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8678">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8678">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8679">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8679">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8680">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8680">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8681">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8681">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8682">11 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8682">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8683">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8683">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8684">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8684">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8685">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8685">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8686">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8686">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8687">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8687">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8688">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8688">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8689">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8689">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8690">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8690">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8691">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8691">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8692">Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8692">Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8693">nip #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8693">nip#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8694">nip</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8694">nip</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8695">numer identyfkocji podatkowej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8695">numer identyfikacji podatkowej</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8696">numeridentyfkocjipodatkowej #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8696">numeridentyfikacjipodatkowej#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8697">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8697">tax id</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8720">Номер карты гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8720">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8721">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8721">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8722">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8722">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8723">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8723">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8724">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8724">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8725">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8725">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8726">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8726">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8727">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8727">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8728">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8728">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8729">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8729">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8730">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8730">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8750">Номер водительского удостоверения для Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8750">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8751">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8751">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8752">два шаблона: две буквы, за которыми следуют 5–8 цифр со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8752">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8753">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8753">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8754">Шаблон 1: две буквы, за которыми следуют 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8754">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8755">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8755">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8756">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8756">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8757">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8757">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8758">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8758">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8759">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8759">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8760">Шаблон 2: одна буква, за которой следуют 6/8 цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8760">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8761">Одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8761">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8762">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8762">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8763">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8763">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8764">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8764">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8765">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8765">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8766">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8766">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8767">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8767">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8768">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8768">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8769">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8769">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8770">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8770">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8771">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8771">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8903">Номер паспорта гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8903">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8904">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8905">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8905">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8906">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8906">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8907">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8907">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8908">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8908">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8909">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8909">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8910">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8910">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8911">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8911">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8912">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8912">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8913">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8913">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8914">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8914">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8915">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8915">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8916">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8916">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8917">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8917">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8918">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8918">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8919">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8919">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8946">Идентификационный номер налога для Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8946">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8947">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8947">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8948">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8948">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8949">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8949">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8950">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8950">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8951">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8951">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8952">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8952">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8953">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8953">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8954">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8954">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8955">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8955">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8956">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8956">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8957">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8957">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8958">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8958">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8959">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8959">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8960">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8960">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8961">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8961">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8962">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8962">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8987">Номер водительского удостоверения в Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8987">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8988">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8988">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8989">один символ, за которым следует восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8989">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8990">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8990">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8991">один символ, за которым следует восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8991">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8992">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8992">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8993">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8993">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8994">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8994">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8995">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8995">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8996">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8996">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8997">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8997">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8998">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8998">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-8999">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-8999">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9127">Личный числовой код Румынии (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9127">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9128">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9128">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9129">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9129">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9130">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9130">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9131">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9131">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9132">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9132">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9133">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9133">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9134">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9134">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9135">13 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9135">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9136">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9136">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9137">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9137">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9138">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9138">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9139">две цифры, которые могут быть 01–52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9139">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9140">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9140">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9141">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9141">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9142">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9142">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9143">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9143">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9144">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9144">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9145">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9145">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9146">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9146">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9147">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9147">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9148">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9148">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9199">Номер паспорта гражданина Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9199">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9200">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9200">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9201">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9201">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9202">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9202">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9203">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9203">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9204">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9204">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9205">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9205">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9206">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9206">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9207">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9207">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9208">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9208">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9209">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9209">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9210">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (пример: 01 FEB/FEB 10) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9210">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9211">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9211">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9212">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9212">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9213">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9213">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9231">Внутренний номер паспорта гражданина России</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9231">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9232">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9232">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9233">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9233">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9234">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9234">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9235">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9235">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9236">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9236">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9237">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9237">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9238">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9238">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9239">10-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9239">10-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9240">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9240">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9241">10-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9241">10-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9242">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9242">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9243">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9243">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9244">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9244">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9245">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9245">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9246">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9246">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9247">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9247">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9248">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9248">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9249">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9249">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9250">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9250">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9251">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9251">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9252">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9252">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9269">Международный номер паспорта гражданина России</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9269">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9270">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9270">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9271">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9271">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9272">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9272">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9273">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9273">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9274">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9274">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9275">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9275">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9276">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9276">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9277">девятизначный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9277">nine-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9278">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9278">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9279">девятизначный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9279">nine-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9280">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9280">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9281">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9281">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9282">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9282">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9283">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9283">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9284">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9284">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9285">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9285">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9286">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9286">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9287">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9287">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9288">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9288">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9293">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9293">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9294">passport id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9294">passport id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9295">passportno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9295">passportno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9298">id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9298">паспорт id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9300">pусский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9300">pусский номер паспорта</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9304">номерпаспорта #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9304">номерпаспорта#</span></span>


## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9305">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9305">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9306">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9306">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9307">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9307">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9308">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9308">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9309">10 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9309">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9310">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9310">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9311">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9311">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9312">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9312">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9313">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9313">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9314">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9314">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9315">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9315">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9316">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9316">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9317">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9317">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9318">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9318">Identification Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9320">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9320">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9321">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9321">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9322">Номер удостоверения личности для национальной регистрации Сингапура (NRIC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9322">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9323">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9323">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9324">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9324">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9325">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9325">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9326">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9326">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9327">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9327">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9328">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9328">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9329">алфавитная проверочные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9329">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9330">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9330">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9331">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9331">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9332">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9332">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9333">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9333">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9334">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9334">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9335">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9335">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9336">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9336">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9337">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9337">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9338">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9338">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9339">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9339">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9340">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9340">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_singapore_nric"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9341">Keyword_singapore_nric</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9341">Keyword_singapore_nric</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9350">Номер водительского удостоверения для Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9350">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9351">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9351">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9352">один символ, за которым следует семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9352">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9353">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9353">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9354">один символ, за которым следует семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9354">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9355">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9355">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9356">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9356">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9357">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9357">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9358">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9358">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9359">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9359">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9360">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9360">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9361">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9361">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9362">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9362">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9363">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9363">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9364">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9364">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9365">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9365">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9366">driverlics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9366">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9367">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9367">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9368">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9368">driverlicenses</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9488">Персональный номер для Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9488">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9489">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9489">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9490">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9490">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9494">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9494">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9495">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9495">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9496">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательные знаки backslash</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9496">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9497">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9497">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9498">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9498">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9499">необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9499">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9500">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9500">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9501">одна необязательная проверотельная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9501">one optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9502">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9502">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9503">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9503">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9504">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9504">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9505">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9505">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9506">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9506">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9507">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9507">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9508">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9508">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9509">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9509">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9556">Номер паспорта гражданина Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9556">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9557">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9557">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9558">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9558">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9559">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9559">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9560">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9560">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9561">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9562">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9562">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9563">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9564">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9564">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9565">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9565">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9566">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9566">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9567">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9567">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9568">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9568">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9569">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9569">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9570">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9570">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9583">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9583">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9592">Номер водительского удостоверения для Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9592">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9593">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9593">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9594">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9594">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9595">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9595">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9596">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9596">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9597">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9597">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9598">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9598">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9599">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9599">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9600">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9600">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9601">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9601">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9602">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9602">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
