## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9729">Уникальный номер гражданина Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9729">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9730">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9730">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9731">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9731">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9732">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9732">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9733">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9733">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9734">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9734">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9735">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9735">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9736">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9736">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9737">13 цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9737">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9738">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9738">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9739">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9739">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9740">семь цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMLLL), где "LLL" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9740">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9741">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9741">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9742">три цифры, соответствующие комбинации пола и серийного номера для людей, которые были в один день (000–499 для детей и 500–999 для детей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9742">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9743">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9743">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9744">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9744">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9745">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9745">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9746">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9746">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9747">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9747">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9748">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9748">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9749">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9749">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9750">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9750">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9751">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9751">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9779">Номер паспорта гражданина Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9779">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9780">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9780">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9781">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9781">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9782">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9782">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9783">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9783">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9784">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9784">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9785">одна буква в верхнем регистре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9785">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9786">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9786">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9787">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9787">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9788">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9788">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9789">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9789">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9790">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9790">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9791">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9791">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9792">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9792">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9793">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9793">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9794">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9794">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9795">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9795">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9796">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9796">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9806">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9806">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9807">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9807">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9808">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9808">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9809">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9809">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9810">гtevilka potnega lista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9810">številka potnega lista</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9811">potek veljavnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9811">potek veljavnosti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9812">список potni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9812">potni list#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9813">datum rojstva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9813">datum rojstva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9814">список potni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9814">potni list</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9819">Идентификационный номер налога для Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9819">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9820">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9820">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9821">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9821">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9822">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9822">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9823">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9823">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9824">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9824">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9825">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9825">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9826">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9826">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9827">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9827">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9828">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9828">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9829">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9829">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9830">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9830">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9831">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9831">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9832">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9832">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9833">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9833">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9834">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9834">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9835">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9835">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9836">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9836">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9837">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9837">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9838">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9838">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9839">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9839">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9863">Идентификационный номер для Южной Африки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9863">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9864">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9865">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9865">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9866">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9867">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9867">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9868">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9868">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9869">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9869">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9870">индикатор гражданства из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9870">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9871">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9871">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9872">одна цифра, которая является цифрой контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9872">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9873">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9873">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9874">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9874">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9875">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9875">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9876">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9876">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9877">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9877">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9878">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9878">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9879">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9879">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9880">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9880">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9881">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9881">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9882">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9882">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9883">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9883">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9884">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9884">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9885">Регистрационный номер резидента Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9885">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9886">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9886">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9887">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9887">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9888">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9888">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9889">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9889">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9890">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9890">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9891">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9891">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9892">одна цифра, определяемая возрастом и полом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9892">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9893">четырехзначный код региона рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9893">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9894">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9894">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9895">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9895">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9896">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9896">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9897">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9897">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9898">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9898">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9899">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9899">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9900">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9900">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9901">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9901">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9902">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9902">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9903">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9903">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9904">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9904">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9905">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9905">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9906">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9906">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9907">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9907">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9908">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9908">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9909">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9909">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9910">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9910">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9911">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9911">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9912">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9912">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9913">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9913">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9914">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9915">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9915">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9916">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9917">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9917">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9918">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9918">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9919">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9919">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9920">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9920">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9921">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9921">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9922">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9922">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9923">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9923">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9924">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9924">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9925">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9925">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9926">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9926">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-9927">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-9927">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10061">DNI для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10061">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10062">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10062">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10063">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10063">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10064">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10064">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10065">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10065">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10066">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10066">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10067">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10067">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10068">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10068">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10069">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10069">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10070">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10070">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10071">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10071">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10072">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10072">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10073">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10073">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10074">одна контрольная буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10074">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10075">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10075">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10076">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10076">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10077">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10077">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10078">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10078">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10079">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10079">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10080">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10080">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10081">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10081">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10082">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10082">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10106">Номер паспорта гражданина Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10106">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10107">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10107">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10108">сочетание букв и чисел из восьми или девяти символов без пробелов или делений.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10108">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10109">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10109">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10110">восьми- или девяти символьное сочетание букв и чисел:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10110">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10111">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10111">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10112">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10112">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10113">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10113">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10114">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10114">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10115">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10115">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10116">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10116">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10117">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10117">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10118">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10118">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10119">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10119">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10120">Регулярное выражение `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД-ММ-YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10120">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10121">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10121">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10122">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10122">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10123">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10123">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10136">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10136">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10141">número de pasaporte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10141">número de pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10142">números pasaporte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10142">números pasaporte</span></span>

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10152">Номер социального обеспечения Испании (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10152">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10153">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в номер социального обеспечения ЕС или тип конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10153">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10154">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10154">It's  available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10155">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10155">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10156">11–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10156">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10157">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10157">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10158">11–12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10158">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10159">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10159">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10160">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10160">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10161">семь-восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10161">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10162">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10162">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10163">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10163">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10164">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10164">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10165">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10165">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10166">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10166">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10167">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10167">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10168">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10168">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10169">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10169">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Spain SSN -->
<Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10170">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10170">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10171">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10171">None</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10172">Идентификационный номер налога для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10172">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10173">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10173">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10174">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10174">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10175">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10175">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10176">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10176">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10177">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10177">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10178">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10178">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10179">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10179">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10180">семь или восемь цифр и одна или две буквы в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10180">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10181">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10181">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10182">Испанские персональные лица с национальные удостоверения личности для Испании:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10182">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10183">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10183">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10184">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10184">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10185">Нерезиденты без национального удостоверения личности для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10185">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10186">одна буква в верхнем регистре "L" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10186">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10187">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10187">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10188">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10188">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10189">Resident Resident Residents under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10189">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10190">одна буква в верхнем регистре "K" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10190">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10191">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10191">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10192">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10192">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10193">Подмена идентификационных номеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10193">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10194">одна буква в верхнем регистре, которая является "X", "Y" или "Z" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10194">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10195">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10195">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10196">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10196">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10197">Подмены без идентификационных номеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10197">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10198">одна буква в верхнем регистре с буквой "M" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10198">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10199">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10199">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10200">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10200">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10201">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10201">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10202">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10202">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10203">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10203">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10204">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10204">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10205">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10205">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10206">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10206">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10207">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10208">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10208">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10239">SQL Server подключения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10239">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10240">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10240">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10241">Строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10241">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10242">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10242">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10243">строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10243">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10244">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10244">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10245">строка "Password" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует строчная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10245">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10246">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10246">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10247">любой символ, который не является знаком доллара ($), символом процента (%), больше символа (>), в символе (@), кавычках ("), точка с зазнаковкой (;), левая скобка ([) или левая скобка ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10247">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10248">любое сочетание 7–128 символов, которые не являются точками с за точками (;) косая черта (/) или кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10248">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10249">точка с зачетом (;) или кавычка (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10249">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10250">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10250">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10251">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10251">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10252">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10252">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10253">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10253">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10254">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10254">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10255">Ключевое слово из CEP_GlobalFilter не найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10255">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10256">Регулярное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10256">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10257">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10257">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10258">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10258">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10259">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10259">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10265">(Обратите внимание, что технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10265">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10266">Пароль или пробел 0–2, знаки равного (=), 0-2 пробела и звездочка (\*) -OR-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10266">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10267">Пароль или pwd, за которым следует:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10267">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10268">Знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10268">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10269">Символ "Меньше символа" (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10269">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10270">Любое сочетание из 1–200 символов, которые являются буквами верхнего или нижнего регистра, цифрами, звездочкой (\*), дефисом (-), подчеркнутой (_) или символом белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10270">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10271">Символ "Больше" (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10271">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10285">Номер водительского удостоверения для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10285">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10286">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10286">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10287">десять цифр, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10287">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10288">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10288">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10289">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10289">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10290">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10290">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10291">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10291">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10292">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10292">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10293">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10293">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10294">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10294">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10295">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10295">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10296">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10296">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10297">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10297">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10298">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10298">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10431">Национальный ИД Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10431">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10432">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10432">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10433">10 или 12 цифр и дополнительный разделитель.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10433">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10434">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10434">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10435">10 или 12 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10435">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10436">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10436">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10437">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10437">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10438">либо "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10438">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10439">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10439">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10440">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10440">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10441">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10441">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10442">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10442">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10443">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10443">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10444">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10444">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10445">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10445">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10446">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10446">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10447">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10447">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10448">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10448">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10449">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10449">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10468">Номер паспорта гражданина Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10468">Sweden passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10469">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10469">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10470">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10470">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10471">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10471">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10472">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10472">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10473">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10473">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10474">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10474">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10475">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10475">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10476">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10476">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10477">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10477">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10478">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10478">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10479">Верно одно из следующих:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10479">one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10480">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10480">a keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10481">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_sweden_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10481">a keyword from Keyword_sweden_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
<Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
