## <a name="sweden-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10512">Номер социального обеспечения швеции или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10512">Sweden social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10513">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального обеспечения ЕС или типе конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10513">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10514">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10514">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10515">12 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10515">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10516">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10516">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10517">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10517">12 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10518">восемь цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYYYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10518">eight digits that correspond to the birth date (YYYYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10519">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10519">three digits that correspond to a serial number where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10520">Последняя цифра в серийном номере указывает пол по назначению нечетного номера для самца и четного номера для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10520">the last digit in the serial number indicates gender by the assignment of an odd number for male and an even number for female</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10521">До 1990 г. назначение серийного номера соответствовало округу, в котором был замещетель номера.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10521">Before 1990, the assignment of a serial number corresponded to the county where the bearer of the number was born.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10522">Или (если это было до 1947 г.), где они были, согласно налоговым записям, 1 января 1947 г. со специальным кодом (обычно 9 в качестве седьмой цифры) для угона.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10522">Or (if born before 1947) where they had been living, according to tax records, on January 1, 1947, with a special code (usually 9 as the seventh digit) for immigrants.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10523">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10523">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10524">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10524">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10525">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10525">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10526">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10526">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10527">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10527">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10528">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10528">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10529">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10529">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10530">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10530">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10531">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10531">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10532">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10532">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10533">Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10533">Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10546">identifikationsnumret #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10546">identifikationsnumret#</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10547">Идентификационный номер налога для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10547">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10548">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10548">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10549">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10549">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10550">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10550">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10551">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10551">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10552">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10552">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10553">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10553">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10554">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10554">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10555">10 цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10555">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10556">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10556">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10557">10 цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10557">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10558">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10558">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10559">знак "плюс" или "минус"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10559">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10560">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10560">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10561">для номеров, выдавшихся до 1990 г., седьмая и восьмая цифры определяют округ рождения или инородных людей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10561">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10562">цифра в девятой позиции указывает пол по нечетным для самцов или даже для самцов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10562">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10563">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10563">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10564">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10564">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10565">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10565">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10566">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10566">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10567">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10567">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10568">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10568">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10569">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10569">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10570">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10570">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10571">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10571">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10597">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10597">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10598">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10598">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10599">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют от 5 до 31 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10599">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10600">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10600">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10601">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют 5–31 буква или цифры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10601">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10602">4-буква банковского кода (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10602">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10603">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10603">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10604">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10604">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10605">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10605">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10606">от одной до трех букв или цифр (оставшаяся часть BBAN);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10606">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10607">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10608">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10608">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10609">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10610">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10611">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10611">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10612">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10612">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10649">Номер АЧЧ для швейцарии SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10649">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10650">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10650">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10651">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10651">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10652">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10652">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10653">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10653">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10654">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10654">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10655">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10655">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10656">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10656">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10657">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10657">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10658">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10658">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10659">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10659">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10660">три цифры — 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10660">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10661">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10661">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10662">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10662">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10663">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10663">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10664">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10664">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10665">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10665">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10666">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10666">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10667">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10667">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10668">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10668">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10669">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10669">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10670">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10670">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10671">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10671">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10672">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10672">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10673">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10673">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10674">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10674">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10695">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10695">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10696">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10696">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10697">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10697">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10698">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10698">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10699">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10699">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10700">одна буква (на английском языке без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10700">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10701">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10701">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10702">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10702">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10703">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10703">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10704">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10704">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10705">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10705">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10706">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10706">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10707">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10707">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10708">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10708">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10709">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10709">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10710">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10710">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10711">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10711">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10712">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10712">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10718">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10718">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10719">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10719">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10720">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10720">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10721">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10721">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10722">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10722">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10723">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10723">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10724">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10724">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10725">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10725">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10726">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10726">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10727">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10727">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10728">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10728">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10729">Номер паспорта гражданина Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10729">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10730">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10730">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10731">биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10731">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10732">Номер не биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10732">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10733">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10733">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10734">биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10734">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10735">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10735">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10736">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10736">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10737">не биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10737">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10738">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10738">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10739">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10739">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10740">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10740">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10741">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10741">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10742">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10742">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10743">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10743">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10744">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10744">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10749">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10749">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10750">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10750">Passport Num</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10755">Номер сертификата резидента Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10755">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10756">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10757">10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10757">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10758">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10759">10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10759">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10760">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10760">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10761">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10761">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10762">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10762">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10763">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10763">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10764">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10764">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10765">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10765">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10766">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10766">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10767">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10767">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10768">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10768">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10769">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10769">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10770">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10770">Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10771">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10771">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10772">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10772">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10773">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10773">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10774">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10774">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10775">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10775">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10776">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10776">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10777">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10777">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10778">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10778">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10779">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10779">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10780">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10780">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10781">Идентификационный код для тайских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10781">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10782">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10782">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10783">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10783">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10784">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10784">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10785">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10785">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10786">первая цифра не нуль или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10786">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10787">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10787">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10788">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10788">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10789">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10789">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10790">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10790">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10791">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10791">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10792">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10792">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10793">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10793">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10794">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10794">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10795">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10795">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10796">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10796">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10797">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10797">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10798">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10798">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10799">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10799">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10800">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10800">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10801">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10801">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10802">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10802">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10803">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10803">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10804">Идентификационный номер гражданина Турецкий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10804">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10805">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10805">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10806">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10806">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10807">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10807">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10808">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10808">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10809">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10809">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10810">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10810">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10811">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10811">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10812">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10812">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10813">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10813">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10814">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10814">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10815">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10815">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10816">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10816">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10817">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10817">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10818">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10818">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10819">TC Kim kim</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10819">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10820">TC Kim numaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10820">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10821">Vatanda vat vatk numaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10821">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10822">Vatanda vat vatk no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10822">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10823">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10823">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10824">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10824">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10825">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ДЛЯ ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10825">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10826">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10826">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10827">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10827">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10828">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10828">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10829">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10829">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10830">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10830">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10831">Пять букв (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10831">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10832">Одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10832">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10833">Пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10833">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10834">Седьмая символа приращена на 50, если драйвер является женщина; для экзаменов: от 51 до 62, а не от 01 до 12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10834">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10835">Две буквы (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10835">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10836">Пять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10836">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10837">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10837">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10838">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10838">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10839">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10839">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10840">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10840">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10841">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10841">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10842">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10842">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10843">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10843">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10844">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10844">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_drivers_license"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10845">Keyword_uk_drivers_license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10845">Keyword_uk_drivers_license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10846">DVLA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10846">DVLA</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10849">motor cars</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10849">motor cars</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10850">125cc</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10850">125cc</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10851">sidecar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10851">sidecar</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10852">трициклы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10852">tricycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10853">10</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10853">motorcycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10854">photocard licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10854">photocard licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10855">learner drivers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10855">learner drivers</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10856">licence holder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10856">licence holder</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10857">licence holders</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10857">licence holders</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10858">driving licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10858">driving licences</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10859">driving licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10859">driving licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10860">dual control car</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10860">dual control car</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10861">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10861">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10862">roll number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10862">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10863">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10863">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10864">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1–4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10864">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10865">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10865">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10866">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют 1-4 числа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10866">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10867">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10867">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10868">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10868">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10869">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10869">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10870">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10870">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10871">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10871">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10872">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10872">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10873">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10873">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10879">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10879">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10880">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10880">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10881">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10881">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10882">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10882">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10883">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10883">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10884">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10884">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10885">3 или 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10885">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10886">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10886">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10887">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10887">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10888">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10888">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10889">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10889">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10890">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10890">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10891">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10891">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10892">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10892">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10893">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10893">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10894">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10894">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10895">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10895">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10896">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10896">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10897">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10897">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10898">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10898">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10899">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10899">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10901">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10901">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10905">health authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10905">health authority</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10907">patient id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10907">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10908">patient identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10908">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10909">patient no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10909">patient no</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10911">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10911">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10912">GP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10912">GP</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10914">D.O.B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10914">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10915">Date of Birth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10915">Date of Birth</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10917">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10917">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10918">national insurance number (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10918">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10919">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации для национального идентификационных номеров ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10919">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10920">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10920">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10921">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10922">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10922">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10923">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10924">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10924">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10925">две буквы (допустимые niNOs используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который проверяется этим шаблоном; без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10925">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10926">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10926">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10927">либо "A", "B", "C", либо "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10927">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10928">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10928">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10929">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10929">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10930">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10930">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10931">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10931">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10932">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10932">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10933">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10933">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10934">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10934">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10935">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10935">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10936">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10936">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10937">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10937">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10938">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10938">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10939">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10939">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10940">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10940">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10941">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10941">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10942">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10942">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10943">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10943">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10944">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10944">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10945">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10945">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10967">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10967">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10968">Уникальный справочный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10968">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10969">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10969">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10970">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10970">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10971">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10971">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10972">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10972">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10973">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10973">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10974">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10974">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10975">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10976">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10976">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10977">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10978">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10978">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10979">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10979">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10980">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10980">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10981">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10981">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10982">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10982">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10983">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10983">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-10984">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-10984">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11004">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11004">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11005">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11005">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11006">6–17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11006">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11007">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11007">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11008">6–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11008">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11009">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11009">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11010">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11010">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11011">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11011">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11012">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11012">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11013">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11013">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11014">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11014">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11044">Номер водительского удостоверения для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11044">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11045">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11045">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11046">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11046">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11047">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11047">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11048">зависит от состояния , например, Нью-Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11048">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11049">будут совпадать девять цифр в формате ddd ddd ddd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11049">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11050">девять цифр, например ddddddddd, не будут совпадать.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11050">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11051">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11051">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11052">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11052">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11053">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11053">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11054">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11055">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11055">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11056">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11056">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11057">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11057">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11058">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11058">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11059">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11059">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11060">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11060">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11061">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11061">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be9b1-11062">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be9b1-11062">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
